Package: gbat
Title: Gene-Based Association Test for Trans-eQTL Discovery
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jinghui", "Li", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identifies trans-associations between genes using cross-validated
    BLUP (Best Linear Unbiased Prediction) predictions and genome-wide
    significance testing with multiple hypothesis correction. Starting from
    a normalized count matrix, the pipeline computes surrogate variables,
    estimates cis-genetic components via REML, predicts genetic values
    (BLUPs), tests trans-associations, and applies FDR control.
